title: Welcome To My Blog
text:
This is my first post in Github. Welcome!

My name is Dian Sheng. I received dual BEng degrees in Electronic Science and Technology from Xi’an Jiaotong – Liverpool University and The University of Liverpool (UoL) with First Class Honors in 2022. Apart from work, I like to watch movies, take a walk, and hike.
